        <name>GetValueText</name>
        <qualifiedname>Dali::Accessibility::Value::GetValueText</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Gets the formatted current value. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This does not have to be <ref refid="classDali_1_1Accessibility_1_1Value_1a109a7f78096cc4b4e1222a792db94c33" kindref="member">GetCurrent()</ref> formatted in any particular way, i.e. it may be an arbitrary string, e.g. &quot;small font size&quot; for the numeric value 10.0.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>The current value as text</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>Only used if the &quot;value_format&quot; attribute is &quot;text&quot; </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Accessibility_1_1Value_1a109a7f78096cc4b4e1222a792db94c33" kindref="member">Value::GetCurrent()</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
